research_name.thaumadditions:wormhole_mirror=Wormhole Mirror
research_stage.thaumadditions:wormhole_mirror.1=WIP
I was wondering how I could stabilize and expand the thin connection between magic mirrors, so I could pass through them... Studying void metal does bring some hints, but I need a bit of additional thinking...
research_stage.thaumadditions:wormhole_mirror.2=WIP
Okay, I have found a way to expand connections between magic mirrors... using a... 'wormhole'? Whatever that is, I really want to test it out, but then I think I'm going crazy... Using a thaumometer (as a connection catcher), a bit of void plates onto the hand mirror seem to get me a Wormhole Mirror... Though, how does it work? Perhaps I should use it on a bound mirror?..
##lets you use linked essentia/magic mirrors as teleporters

research_name.thaumadditions:void_crop=Growing Void
research_stage.thaumadditions:void_crop.1=WIP
Void seeds have a wonderful ability to regenerate. But could this matter be directed to cloning these rare seeds?
research_stage.thaumadditions:void_crop.2=WIP
Infusing void seeds with primordial energies have enabled me to make the seed plantable. I'll need a complex and long infusion process to get it done.
##grows Void Seeds (the matching names are annoying) and rarely a Void Fruit, which completely fills saturation

research_name.thaumadditions:essentia_pistol=Essentia Pistol
research_stage.thaumadditions:essentia_pistol.1=WIP
Dispersing salts is nice, but not very applicable in rather unexpected situations I might end up in. Making it portable would be a key requirement to success.
research_stage.thaumadditions:essentia_pistol.2=WIP
Using aura disperser as an accelerator is a smart decision. Essentia Pistol would be definitely the best option I could think of. Thaumium would help the essentia travel through the tube safer. I would require something that can hold liquid essentia - something that I already use when infusing items on runic matrix.
