research_name.thaumadditions:shadow_beam_staff=Shadow Beam Staff
research_stage.thaumadditions:shadow_beam_staff.1=WIP
Mithrillium holds so much power, that I could probably focus it into a beam!
research_stage.thaumadditions:shadow_beam_staff.2=WIP
Using vis resonator with mithrillium allows to harness the Alienis into a powerful laser. To charge it, I would need to use Essentia Sink to fill it up with Alienis essentia. Strangely enough, the laser seem to bounce from any surfaces that it hits.
